        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36050753/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36050753/" class="">第25页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/24763456/" class=" " title="丸子">丸子</a>
                (travel in silence~)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36050753">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有一年春天是妈妈下的细面，很温顺地卧在碗里，撒了小葱，滴了酱油，汤面上浮着薄圆的油圈。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-09-05 00:09</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>有一年春天是妈妈下的细面，很温顺地卧在碗里，撒了小葱，滴了酱油，汤面上浮着薄圆的油圈。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







