          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36050667/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36050667/" class="">第21页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/24763456/" class=" " title="丸子">丸子</a>
                (travel in silence~)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36050667">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">乡间所采集的野食，大多有这样未经驯服的青莽之气，或苦后回甘，或甜中带酸，却正是其好处所在。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-09-04 23:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>乡间所采集的野食，大多有这样未经驯服的青莽之气，或苦后回甘，或甜中带酸，却正是其好处所在。</q></blockquote>
